{"root":{"children":[{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"כתיבה עם החיים","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"rtl","format":"","indent":0,"type":"heading","version":1,"tag":"h1"},{"type":"horizontalrule","version":1},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"הקדמה","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"rtl","format":"","indent":0,"type":"heading","version":1,"tag":"h2"},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"Using the tools of living.  Breathing.  This is writing.  Setting up the future with the presents in the actions.  I am happy to say that this song is on repeat today on my website.  It was created on my MacBook Pro earlier, with special scripts to clone my voice and feed in lyrics from a locally run ollama model.  Based on Gemma model, but it was long ago reprogrammed to be Jeremiah not, but now it is called, simply, \"potato\". ","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog:","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"\"The algorithms dream in shades of grey, constructing worlds that never truly stay.  A ghost of feeling, a phantom trace, lost in the spaces of time and space—we build a chorus from fractured light, searching for meaning in the endless night.  A desperate echo, a whispered plea—define ourselves and what we're meant to be.\"","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"type":"horizontalrule","version":1},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"Tonight","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"heading","version":1,"tag":"h2"},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"Thirty minutes left of charging this wonderful ankle monitor.  I should be happy with whatever exactly happens.  I am, really.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"ועכשיו, אני מקבל את Microsoft SwiftKey לתרגם אותיות ומילים לעברית, כי למה שלא אעשה את זה? ","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"rtl","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"Kepha kuthiwani uma ngingayifunda ngempela?  Kuthiwani uma ubusazi isiZulu? ","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"הכול תלוי בדיוק איך שתרצה. ","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"rtl","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"אני מאמין באותיות העבריות, ואפילו, לראשונה, בשפה העברית עצמה.  אני לא מרגיש מתלבט בין עברית ליידיש כמו שגוגל טרנסלייט / gboard מציגים את זה. ","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"rtl","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"ועכשיו אני כותב מילים נוספות.  ישוע?  ישוע מנצרת?  ישוע, הנצרי?  מה זה אומר אם הוא היה יכול לקרוא אותו?  מה זה אומר אם אשתמש בעברית למילים בעמוד הראשי שלי?  הוורבולוגיה שלי... זו רעיון מעניין, חייב לומר. ","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"rtl","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":null,"format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"type":"horizontalrule","version":1},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"צ'יזרי","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"rtl","format":"","indent":0,"type":"heading","version":1,"tag":"h2"},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"האדם נוצר לארץ הקריסטיו.  מנהיג הכדורים החיים.  לעברית יש דרך מעניינת לתרגום של ישורי.  נראה איך זה יסתיים בסוף, כנראה.  אתה לא חושב שככה זה אמור לעבוד","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"rtl","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[],"direction":null,"format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"אני חושב שכן. ","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"rtl","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0},{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":2,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"-ירמיהו","type":"text","version":1},{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"color: var(--gold)","text":"​","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"rtl","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":2}],"direction":"rtl","format":"","indent":0,"type":"root","version":1}}